			<div class="text" id="comment-73016212126">

				<strong class="title">Song Meaning</strong>I remember hearing somewhere that Dylan said that when he wrote this song, he thought it would  be one of the last ones he ever wrote, because he thought that a nuclear war was coming, and everyone would die. So, the surreal imagery in the verses are all the ideas he had left for songs, all the songs he though he wouldn't live to write.				
